- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the performance and complexity of creative telescoping implementations. 
- cs.CA (Computational Geometry) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves bounding formulas and estimation of degrees. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also a possibility as the paper involves mathematical reasoning and deduction.
